	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>The [[lookup @name lowercase]] makes one bite attack against a Medium or smaller target it is grappling. On a hit, the target is swallowed, and the grapple ends.</em></p><p><strong>Swallowed:</strong> The creature is blinded and restrained, has total cover from attacks and effects outside the [[lookup @name lowercase]], and takes [[/r 3d6]] acid damage at the start of each of the [[lookup @name lowercase]]'s turns. The [[lookup @name lowercase]] can have only one creature swallowed at a time.</p><p><strong>Escape:</strong> If the [[lookup @name lowercase]] dies, the swallowed creature is no longer restrained and can spend 5 feet of movement to exit the corpse, ending up prone.</p>",
